#: src/libslic3r/PrintConfig.cpp:802 src/slic3r/GUI/Sidebar.cpp:6770
msgid "Enable manual fan speeds"
msgstr "啟用手動風扇轉速"

#: src/libslic3r/PrintConfig.cpp:803
msgid ""
"When enabled, use the manual fan speed values below for each feature type. "
"This disables dynamic overhang fan speeds to prevent conflicting fan "
"commands. Useful for fine-tuned control over fan behavior per feature."
msgstr ""
"啟用後，會對各特徵類型使用下方的手動風扇轉速值。這會停用動態懸空風扇轉速，以"
"避免衝突的風扇指令。適合對各特徵的風扇行為進行精細控制。"

#: src/libslic3r/PrintConfig.cpp:810 src/libslic3r/PrintConfig.cpp:1551
msgid "Overhang perimeters"
msgstr "懸空輪廓"

#: src/libslic3r/PrintConfig.cpp:811
msgid ""
"Fan speed for overhang perimeters. Used in both auto cooling and manual fan "
"modes. In auto mode, this overrides the bridge fan speed specifically for "
"overhang perimeters. Set to 0 to use no fan for this feature type."
msgstr ""
"懸空輪廓的風扇轉速。於自動冷卻與手動風扇模式皆適用。在自動模式下，這會針對懸"
"空輪廓覆寫橋接風扇轉速。設為 0 則此特徵類型不使用風扇。"

#: src/libslic3r/PrintConfig.cpp:821 src/slic3r/GUI/Tab.cpp:1898
msgid "Interlocking perimeters"
msgstr "互鎖輪廓"

#: src/libslic3r/PrintConfig.cpp:822
msgid ""
"Fan speed for interlocking perimeters when auto cooling is disabled. Set to "
"0 to use no fan for this feature type."
msgstr "停用自動冷卻時，互鎖輪廓的風扇轉速。設為 0 則此特徵類型不使用風扇。"

#: src/libslic3r/PrintConfig.cpp:831 src/libslic3r/PrintConfig.cpp:1358
#: src/libslic3r/PrintConfig.cpp:1371 src/libslic3r/PrintConfig.cpp:2261
#: src/libslic3r/PrintConfig.cpp:3352 src/slic3r/GUI/Sidebar.cpp:2023
#: src/slic3r/GUI/Sidebar.cpp:2069 src/slic3r/GUI/Sidebar.cpp:2232
msgid "External perimeters"
msgstr "外部邊緣"

#: src/libslic3r/PrintConfig.cpp:832
msgid ""
"Fan speed for external perimeters when auto cooling is disabled. Set to 0 to "
"use no fan for this feature type."
msgstr "停用自動冷卻時，外輪廓的風扇轉速。設為 0 則此特徵類型不使用風扇。"

#: src/libslic3r/PrintConfig.cpp:841
msgid "Internal perimeters"
msgstr "內輪廓"

#: src/libslic3r/PrintConfig.cpp:842
msgid ""
"Fan speed for internal perimeters when auto cooling is disabled. Set to 0 to "
"use no fan for this feature type."
msgstr "停用自動冷卻時，內輪廓的風扇轉速。設為 0 則此特徵類型不使用風扇。"

#: src/libslic3r/PrintConfig.cpp:852
msgid ""
"Fan speed for top solid infill when auto cooling is disabled. Set to 0 to "
"use no fan for this feature type."
msgstr ""
"停用自動冷卻時，頂部實心填充的風扇轉速。設為 0 則此特徵類型不使用風扇。"

#: src/libslic3r/PrintConfig.cpp:862
msgid ""
"Fan speed for solid infill (not top) when auto cooling is disabled. Set to 0 "
"to use no fan for this feature type."
msgstr ""
"停用自動冷卻時，實心填充（非頂部）的風扇轉速。設為 0 則此特徵類型不使用風扇。"

#: src/libslic3r/PrintConfig.cpp:871
msgid "Sparse infill"
msgstr "稀疏填充"

#: src/libslic3r/PrintConfig.cpp:872
msgid ""
"Fan speed for sparse internal infill when auto cooling is disabled. Set to 0 "
"to use no fan for this feature type."
msgstr ""
"停用自動冷卻時，稀疏內部填充的風扇轉速。設為 0 則此特徵類型不使用風扇。"

#: src/libslic3r/PrintConfig.cpp:882
msgid ""
"Fan speed for ironing passes when auto cooling is disabled. Set to 0 to use "
"no fan for this feature type."
msgstr "停用自動冷卻時，熨燙行程的風扇轉速。設為 0 則此特徵類型不使用風扇。"

#: src/libslic3r/PrintConfig.cpp:892
msgid ""
"Fan speed for skirt and brim when auto cooling is disabled. Set to 0 to use "
"no fan for this feature type."
msgstr ""
"停用自動冷卻時，外圍裙與邊緣的風扇轉速。設為 0 則此特徵類型不使用風扇。"

#: src/libslic3r/PrintConfig.cpp:902
msgid ""
"Fan speed for support material when auto cooling is disabled. Set to 0 to "
"use no fan for this feature type."
msgstr "停用自動冷卻時，支撐材料的風扇轉速。設為 0 則此特徵類型不使用風扇。"

#: src/libslic3r/PrintConfig.cpp:912
msgid ""
"Fan speed for support interface when auto cooling is disabled. Set to 0 to "
"use no fan for this feature type."
msgstr "停用自動冷卻時，支撐介面的風扇轉速。設為 0 則此特徵類型不使用風扇。"

#: src/libslic3r/PrintConfig.cpp:921 src/slic3r/GUI/Sidebar.cpp:2259
msgid "Bridge flow ratio"
msgstr "橋接流量比"

#: src/libslic3r/PrintConfig.cpp:923
msgid ""
"This factor affects the amount of plastic for bridging. You can decrease it "
"slightly to pull the extrudates and prevent sagging, although default "
"settings are usually good and you should experiment with cooling (use a fan) "
"before tweaking this."
msgstr ""
"該因素會影響用於橋接的塑料流量。您可以稍微降低它以拉出擠出物並防止下垂，儘管"
"預設設定通常很好，您應該在調整這個之前先嘗試使用冷卻（使用風扇）的方式。"

#: src/libslic3r/PrintConfig.cpp:936
msgid ""
"Set this to a non-zero value to set a manual extrusion width for bridges. "
"Bridges print in mid-air and cannot squish against a layer below, so using a "
"narrower width (around nozzle diameter) produces better results than the "
"wider solid infill width. If left zero, solid infill extrusion width will be "
"used. If expressed as percentage (for example 110%) it will be computed over "
"nozzle diameter or layer height, depending on the 'Percentages relative to "
"nozzle size' setting."
msgstr ""
"設為非零值可為橋接手動設定擠出寬度。橋接在空中列印，無法擠壓在下方層上，因此"
"使用較窄的寬度（約噴嘴直徑）比使用較寬的實心填充寬度效果更好。若維持 0，則使"
"用實心填充擠出寬度。若以百分比表示（例如 110%），則依「百分比相對於噴嘴尺寸」"
"設定，以噴嘴直徑或層高計算。"

#: src/libslic3r/PrintConfig.cpp:948
msgid "Single perimeter on top surfaces"
msgstr "頂面單輪廓"

#: src/libslic3r/PrintConfig.cpp:951
msgid ""
"Use only one perimeter on flat top surface, to give more space to the top "
"infill pattern. Could be applied on topmost surface or all top surfaces."
msgstr ""
"在平坦頂面僅使用一道輪廓，為頂部填充圖案留出更多空間。可套用於最頂面或所有頂"
"面。"

