#: src/slic3r/GUI/WipeTowerDialog.cpp:38
msgid "Ramming customization"
msgstr "衝壓擠出自定義"

#: src/slic3r/GUI/WipeTowerDialog.cpp:86
msgid ""
"Ramming denotes the rapid extrusion just before a tool change in a single-"
"extruder MM printer. Its purpose is to properly shape the end of the "
"unloaded filament so it does not prevent insertion of the new filament and "
"can itself be reinserted later. This phase is important and different "
"materials can require different extrusion speeds to get the good shape. For "
"this reason, the extrusion rates during ramming are adjustable.\n"
"\n"
"This is an expert-level setting, incorrect adjustment will likely lead to "
"jams, extruder wheel grinding into filament etc."
msgstr ""
"衝壓擠出表示在單擠出機 MM 打印機中替換工具之前的快速擠出。其目的是正確塑造未"
"加載線材的末端，這樣它就不會妨礙新線材的插入，並且可以在以後重新插入。這個階"
"段很重要，不同的材料可能需要不同的擠壓速度才能獲得良好的形狀。因此，衝壓擠出"
"過程中的擠壓率是可調的。\n"
"\n"
"這是一個專家級的設定，不正確的調整可能會導致卡線、被擠出機齒輪磨成細線等。"

#: src/slic3r/GUI/WipeTowerDialog.cpp:151
msgid "Total ramming time"
msgstr "總衝壓擠出時間"

#: src/slic3r/GUI/WipeTowerDialog.cpp:155
msgid "Total rammed volume"
msgstr "總衝壓擠出量"

#: src/slic3r/GUI/WipeTowerDialog.cpp:161
msgid "Ramming line width"
msgstr "衝壓擠出線寬"

#: src/slic3r/GUI/WipeTowerDialog.cpp:164
msgid "Ramming line spacing"
msgstr "衝壓擠出線間距"

#: src/slic3r/GUI/WipeTowerDialog.cpp:175
#, boost-format
msgid "For constant flow rate, hold %1% while dragging."
msgstr "若要使用固定流量，拖曳時請按住 %1%。"

#: src/slic3r/GUI/WipeTowerDialog.cpp:236
msgid "Wipe tower - Purging volume adjustment"
msgstr "擦拭塔 - 清洗量調整"

#: src/slic3r/GUI/WipeTowerDialog.cpp:241
